@model IList<CriptoCurrencyResearch.Models.Currency>


<h4>What currency do you invest in?</h4>
<hr />
<form asp-controller="Currencies" asp-action="ChoiceCurrencies" method="post" class="form-group">
    @{
        for (int i = 0; i < Model.Count(); i++)
        {
            <input asp-for="@Model[i].CheckboxChecked" type="checkbox" />
            <label asp-for="@Model[i].CurrencyId">@Model[i].Name</label>
            <input asp-for="@Model[i].CurrencyId" type="hidden" />
            <input asp-for="@Model[i].Name" type="hidden" />

            <br />
        }

        <input type="submit" value="Send" class="btn btn-default" />
    }
</form>